/var @name = "World"

/run cmd(@name):/tmp { echo ok }
/run sh(@name):/tmp { echo ok }

=== START TOKENS ===
@name --> variable[declaration]
= --> operator
"World" --> string
cmd --> label
( --> operator
@name --> variable
) --> operator
: --> operator
/ --> string
tmp --> string
sh --> label
( --> operator
@name --> variable
) --> operator
: --> operator
/ --> string
tmp --> string
=== END TOKENS ===
